                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-802-18500408 t18500408-802-punishment-106"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Platt.</hi>
